data.description: Welcome to this delightful ranch-style home nestled in a quiet neighborhood with a backdrop of a lush farmer's field and majestic trees. This 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home offers a peaceful retreat while being conveniently located close to major streets for an effortless commute. The home is designed with comfort in mind. The primary bedroom is strategically positioned on the opposite side of the house from the other bedrooms, ensuring privacy and tranquility. Sunlight streams through every room, creating an inviting and warm atmosphere throughout the day. Enjoy the beauty of natural light in every corner of your new home. The living room and kitchen boast impressive vaulted ceilings that not only enhance the overall aesthetic but also create a sense of openness and spaciousness. The kitchen is a chef's delight with modern stainless steel appliances including a gas range.  A spacious heated two and a half car garage provides convenient parking and extra storage space or room for hobbies. Nearby parks, schools, and shopping centers offer entertainment and convenience.
